{
  "stem": "27335.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They came to the service, and the Gestapo Nationals was right there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that was-- it happened at 1 o'clock when-- and then, I paid.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I just walked out to the street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there was, already, the street was full of people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they were debating, discussing, and yelling, and shouting, and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I started to walk toward the station, the Western station.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And when I went into the station, people were like-- just like sardines, already, in the station.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I decided, well, there's no-- no way back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I tried to make a telephone call-- not to-- Mrs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Tigany had no telephone call, but her friend, a wife of a doctor, who was another-- another contact.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I met her once.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And she mentioned Hannah Szenes' name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But it's-- a side story is too much there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But I heard it from-- from her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I had to pretend that I never hear-- hear the name.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But I head that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I suspected that she's in here somewhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But by that time, she was-- she was in prison.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But anyway, when I walked into the-- into the station, bought a ticket back to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And the train-- the train pulled out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But it was so jammed on a second class ticket, that I was very early, lined up very early.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I was sitting in the upholstered seats there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I was just there alone, yet, for a-- for a few.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And somebody walked into the-- walked into the-- into the porter there on the train and opened up the the English newspaper.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I just looked at it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had to make a fast, fast decision.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Shall I reveal myself?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I-- I just-- I just kept quiet.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
